title: Doom Bots Icons???
body:
I won a doom bots game but _I didn't get an icon_ :( {{item:3070}}

also the sacrifice minions game doesnt work

replies.body: Doom bot icons are still being distributed!  Per the [teemoing](http://na.leagueoflegends.com/en/featured/skins/the-teemoing-2016) announcement, we aim to finish sending them out by the 17th.  Some players may get it before others!  Let me know if you have any questions.
If we win "the teemoing" mode of the doom bots are we eligible to get the little devil teemo icon?
The type of mode you selected won't disqualify you, so you'll be fine!
I don't have mine yet either D:
If you have a touch-screen the mouse won't work for the sacrifice minions game, only the touch-screen will.  (idk if that's what's wrong, but that's what happened to me)

I have defeated Little Devil Teemo in the teemoing and still haven't recieved my little devil teemo icon i defeated him on multiple occasions and i havent recieved it and also do you not recieve it if your disoconnected and the game ends as a lose for your team?
It can take up to two weeks after November 3rd for the Teemoing icons to be added to your account.
